OL,3,CFiles and money seized by regulator in
OL,4,Caftermath of PM Law closure
OL,6,FLegal files and money relating to tens
OL,7,Fof thousands of active cases have been
OL,8,Fseized by the Solicitors Regulation
OL,9,FAuthority (SRA), as the fallout of the
OL,10,Fsudden closure of PM Law Group
OL,11,Fcontinues.
OL,13,FThe Sheffield-based company operated
OL,14,Fdozens of legal brands across the
OL,15,Fcountry, including four branches of
OL,16,FButterworths Solicitors in Cumbria.
OL,18,FThe firm shut suddenly on Monday 2
OL,19,FFebruary, leaving clients in the dark
OL,20,Fabout the future of their legal cases.
