OL,4,Caftermath of PM Law closure
OL,6,FThe SRA has since issued an update on
OL,7,Fthe situation, explaining the action
OL,8,Fit has taken to support PM Law's
OL,9,Fformer clients.
OL,11,FThe SRA has attended 24 PM Law offices
OL,12,Fin Yorkshire, Cumbria, Berkshire and
OL,13,FDerbyshire, and taken possession of
OL,14,Fclient files and funds.
OL,16,FEmergency payments have begun to be
OL,17,Fmade to clients in urgent need, and
OL,18,Fthe SRA has received over 50
OL,19,Fapplications for money from this fund.
