OL,6,FMore than 100 clients have been
OL,7,Fcontacted by the SRA over 'urgent
OL,8,Fmatters', mainly relating to
OL,9,Fconveyancing and litigation matters.
OL,11,FThe SRA has also contacted more than
OL,12,F100 courts to notify them of the
OL,13,Ffirm's closure, and what impact this
OL,14,Fmight have on urgent litigation
OL,15,Fmatters.
OL,17,FGordons LLP is now working on behalf
OL,18,Fof the SRA to advise former clients of
OL,19,Fthe need to find new legal
OL,20,Frepresentation.
