OL,6,FOn a web page dedicated to former PM
OL,7,FLaw clients, Gordons notes its role
OL,8,F"is not to take over acting/carry out
OL,9,Fthe legal work on the individual
OL,10,Fmatters/cases", and that "initially we
OL,11,Fmust prioritise guiding and supporting
OL,12,Fthose clients who are in the most
OL,13,Furgent need."
