OL,6,FPaul Hastings, SRA Director of Client
OL,7,FProtection said: "We have been working
OL,8,Fhard to protect the people impacted by
OL,9,Fthe closure of PM Law. Our
OL,10,Fintervention agent has identified tens
OL,11,Fof thousands of live cases, many of
OL,12,Fwhich involve sensitive and important
OL,13,Fmatters such as personal injury
OL,14,Fclaims, house sales, and probate
OL,15,Fissues.
OL,17,F"We appreciate that this may be a
OL,18,Fstressful time. Clients can rest
OL,19,Fassured that our agents are diligently
OL,20,Fworkingthrough these files to
OL,21,Fidentify and contact them.
