OL,6,F"Our goal is to get to everyone as
OL,7,Fsoon as possible, prioritising those
OL,8,Fin most urgent need. We have, for
OL,9,Fexample, madeseveralemergency grants
OL,10,Ftoallow clients to move house when
OL,11,Fthey hadalready exchangedcontracts."
OL,13,FThe Solicitors Regulation Authority's
OL,14,Finvestigation into PM Law continues.
